&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Gelfand, Rennert &amp;amp; Feldman is seeking a Business Services Administrator with mailroom experience to join our team of dedicated professionals. The Business Services Administrator will be responsible for aiding with all mailroom processes, as well as general operational support. This position is based fully in-office out of our Century City, CA or Encino, CA office.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Receive shipments from various couriers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scan, file, and distribute mail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pick up and route mail to appropriate locations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with off-site storage files&lt;/li&gt;
