&lt;li&gt;Distribute and maintain stock of office supplies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restock mail drops&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other projects and duties as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
