&lt;li&gt;Experience scanning mail or documents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High School Diploma or GED equivalent is required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills (in person, on the phone, and via email)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong computer skills including, Microsoft Office Suite (Excel, Word, Outlook, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A team player with high attention to detail, especially when working on multiple tasks or assignments with competing deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
